text: Great meeting Monday with Barbara Simmons of the #PeaceCenter and Victim Advocate Dori Dugan in #Langhorne to collaborate on ways to get several of my gun safety bills, to include HR4240 and HR4168, advanced in the House. (1/3)
I commend the investigative team for their commitment to bringing to justice those hostile actors who seek to undermine our institutions and our elections.

We pray as a nation for all of the victims and families devastated by the Parkland school shooting. We must not allow yet another tragedy to go unanswered. It is incumbent upon all of us to identify the root causes of this senseless violence and move to address it immediately.

Roughly 50% of small biz are women-owned and small biz accounted for 2/3 of net new jobs over the past 20 yrs. #smallbusinesswee
There are more than 29 million small businesses in the United States. #smallbusinessweek
Small businesses are responsible for creating 63% of new jobs! #smallbusinessweek
